data.description: ASSUMABLE VA, CONVENTIONAL, OR INVESTMENT LOAN AT 2.875 INTEREST RATE! Fabulous 4 bedroom, 3 bathroom home with a one bedroom, one bathroom in-law suite, pool house or guest house. .89 of an acre of beautiful mature trees in a quiet neighborhood.  Wait until you see the pool! Pool is so inviting with a covered lanai area and was recently remodeled with sealed pavers, new motor, tank and and heater. Home features a large living room, separate dining room and wonderful updated kitchen with granite counters. New appliances. New flooring, interior paint, bathroom remodel, plumbing upgrades, interior paint in 2022. Gutters on both units and security system also newer. New water heater, new roof, new energy efficient windows, new HVAC systems in both units completed in 2021. The oversized 2 car garage was enclosed for a bonus room and can easily be returned in to a garage as door is still in tact. Bring the large family, bring Mom and there is room for Dad as well!  Be ready to love where you live.
